commit.message: dot11: Move channel test to source block where it belongs

dot11: Don't apply string channels to source devices when they're not
to-ds

phyviews: Add ability to hide a phy from the UI view, so that phy-like
handlers that don't detect devices don't clutter up the ux
datasource: Remove debug print

capframework: More cleanup around signal handling and monitoring
radview: Remove debug print
capframework: Fix signal masking and handling in general

capframework: Monitor and kill the monitored pid as well as any ipc
child pids

capsource: Handle control-c killing monitored processes in reconnect
mode
datasources:  General cleanup while debugging
radview: Functional JSON sender

radview: Start adding datasource for radview geiger counters (currently
does nothing)
adsbproxy: Properly call initializers for adsbproxy

capframework: Dont strdump junk buffer in some situations, clean up
ordering
nrf: Explicitly set spectrum pointer to null
datasource: Set device as closed when close() is called outside of error
ringbuf: Add byte search function
ui: Default to last time seen sorting on new prefs
adsb: Convert packetchain to captureless-lambda function pointers

packetchain: Remove std::function use from all packet chains, remove api
option entirely.  Convert any existing std::function lambdas to
non-capturing function pointers passable to the traditional packetchain
callbacks.

json: Convert json name conversion to template/functor instead of
std::function to improve speed

pcapng: Add option to truncate duplicate packets to just radiotap
headers
pcapng: Convert filter and selection from std::function to functor, with
the hopes of a significant speed improvement in per-packet callbacks
ux: Turn off fit-columns because it looks terrible on tiny screens

ux: While funny, turn off comic sans effect on create api key (artifact
of font-awesome update)

fix accidental reversal

obviously be 802.15.4
